title: Schedule A Tour To See Our Newly Renovated Apartment Homes/Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
